article_text:
Wichita Police are also searching for the suspects involved in a home robbery.

It happened around 1:30 a.m. Saturday in the 2400 Block of East Shadybrook.

An 18 year-old male was approached by two males while sitting in his car. One of the suspects had a gun and demanded the victim to get out of the car.

Police say the victim was kicked and punched by the suspects before they stole his car,

Victim was treated for minor injuries

Police are still searching for the car. it's a black 4 door '98 Acura TL. The tag number is 413HJM,

If you spot that car with that tag number, you are asked to call 911
